  "detailed_description": "A Puzzle Action Game Based On Green.<br />\r\nThe player changes in three steps depending on the proportion of the stage reflected in the camera, and the size and jumping power change with the change.<br />\r\nAlso, some blocks appear when the stage is shown, and some blocks appear when a specific block is shown.<br />\r\nLet's guide the player to the goal by considering where to project on the stage considering these gimmicks.(Google Translation)",
